471
00:34:06,072 --> 00:34:07,365
Uma água?

472
00:34:07,990 --> 00:34:09,075
Claro, pode ser.

473
00:34:13,121 --> 00:34:14,956
- Ficou bom.
- Valeu.

474
00:34:15,581 --> 00:34:18,501
